# Vendored lcms2 C source (downloaded by bench/lcms_c/fetch-lcms2.sh).
# We commit the bench glue (bench_lcms.c / Makefile / README / fetch
# scripts) but NOT the third-party lcms2 source tree — too big, has
# its own upstream.
/bench/lcms_c/lcms2-2.18/
/bench/lcms_c/lcms2-2.19/
/bench/lcms_c/lcms2-*/
/bench/lcms_c/*.o
/bench/lcms_c/bench_lcms
/bench/lcms_c/bench_lcms.exe

# lcms_compat/ harness — profiles are licensed artefacts (Adobe,
# IDEAlliance, ECI, RISO, etc.) so user-supplied copies stay local;
# reference .it8 data is derived measurement data and IS committed.
# See bench/lcms_compat/profiles/README.md for the licensing split.
/bench/lcms_compat/profiles/*
!/bench/lcms_compat/profiles/README.md

# Scratch / work-in-progress instrumented lcms2 tree — will be
# distilled down to a patch file under bench/lcms_compat/lcms_patch/
# in v1.5 (deferred from v1.3 to keep the release scoped), at which
# point this whole folder goes away.
/bench/lcms_exposed/
